divs: Sighting DetailsAfter me and a few friends got off the church bus, we heard a loud high pitch noise, looking up above my dads garage, around my uncles house on the hill side, we all say a ufo. It was green and blue, more blue, sphere with a black hole like in the middle. It was falling straight down, it had a tail fowling it. Its landed but no one has traveled up the hill to look.
